data.title: James Dyrenforth
data.meta_description: James Dyrenforth was born on January 31, 1895 in Chicago, Illinois, USA. He was an actor, known for Lolita (1962), A Night to Remember (1958) and The City of the Dead (1960). He died on December 26, 1973 in London, England.
